FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Everything you need to know about our toilet paper marketplace
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: How does your toilet paper marketplace work?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our marketplace connects toilet paper buyers with sellers, offering a wide variety of brands, types, and quantities. Users can browse, compare prices, and make purchases securely through our platform.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: What types of toilet paper do you offer?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: We offer a diverse range of toilet paper products, including eco-friendly, ultra-soft, quilted, and budget options. Our sellers provide both residential and commercial toilet paper in various pack sizes.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: How do you ensure the quality of toilet paper sold?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: We work with reputable sellers and encourage customer reviews. All products must meet our quality standards, and we have a return policy in place for any unsatisfactory purchases.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: Do you offer bulk purchasing options?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Yes, we cater to both individual consumers and businesses. Many of our sellers offer bulk purchasing options at competitive prices, perfect for large families, offices, or commercial establishments.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: How do you handle shipping and delivery?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: Shipping methods and costs vary depending on the seller and your location. Many sellers offer free shipping on orders above a certain amount. You can view shipping details on each product page before making a purchase.
